text: Sir Richard Sherborn (by 1522-94), of Stonyhurst, Lancashire, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Lancashire in October 1553, Preston in November 1554 and 1558, and Liverpool in 1555. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:1594 deaths Category:Members of the Parliament of England (pre-1707) for Lancashire Category:English MPs 1553 (Mary I) Category:English MPs 1554–1555 Category:English MPs 1555 Category:English MPs 1558 Category:Members of the Parliament of England (pre-1707) for Liverpool
